00:14:54.571 --> 00:14:54.880
I just think it's interesting because whenever the Lord gives me these cues and has me praying, it's important.

00:14:54.880 --> 00:14:58.506
God does not speak just to hear himself talk.

00:15:13.400 --> 00:15:13.787
